Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:06.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:08.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:29.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:12.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:16.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:34.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:39.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:05.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:32.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the thing about phoenixes:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the hardship,\Nthey always rise back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're reborn even stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, men! I was a foolish\Ncaptain who couldn't live up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the trust my precious friend placed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But I wanna let...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Vigaro see it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to see our flag flying\Nabove the ocean where he's at rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give back my flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Luffy is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's come for our Jolly Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We can still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I don't know how\NLuffy learned about the flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not as though he\Nwitnessed it getting stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Which means we've still got a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know where the Jolly Roger is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far more reliable\Nthan that lame moss head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to become my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do and I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a fool of the Accino Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one who stole\Nour Jolly Roger, Naked Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! So what if I did, whippersnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your butt right\Nquick and get our flag back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:05:03.20,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Super Hot-Hot Final Battle!\NLuffy vs. the Scorching Hot Don"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So you're a Devil\NFruit power holder, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly has been a long time\Nsince I personally hunted a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be honored, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Accino...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the head of that\Nfamily of bounty hunters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of powers did he\Nget from the Hot-Hot Fruit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault that the temperature\Nhas been going up and down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kick my butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back, I've met countless\Npirates who've made that same claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Each and every one...\N--Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should let me finish talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can melt... anything I touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still think you can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's attacks aren't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't even touched the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't lay so much as a finger on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too hot to punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lookie! Slip, slip, slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:07:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even do stuff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My entire body is suspended\Nby the tiny bit of steam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,emitted from the ice melted\Nby the soles of my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! That's so neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slippity-slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slip around like fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wahoo!\N--Screech!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Hot-Hot ability isn't all that bad after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I should have expected\Nfrom a 300-million Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good at what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the real fight has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot Makeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see a thing! What's he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot-Fried Tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our flags are somewhere inside that house...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I only love my children!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naked Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw a hissy fit. I'll play with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready for the finishing move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steam...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We can't afford to let\NPapa's temper grow any hotter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa is going to claim\NStraw Hat's head, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I need to\Ntake out this 100-Berry-bounty,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can lift his spirits\Nback up as much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't hand my head\Nover to a lowly bounty hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, you may think you're\Nfighting on par with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the tables are about to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm frozen to the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, is this the best the\NPhoenix Pirates can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's about time I took your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't take any damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was burning hot at first, but luckily\Nthe ice cooled me right off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? This time I'll melt\Nyour entire body in a flash...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I don't have to endure any\Nmore of your insolent garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Level Up: 3,000 Degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an impressive amount of smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't touch you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! He went flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to be rejoicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Luffy will go after\Nthe Jolly Roger in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Crap! He'll find out that\Nthey stole our flag for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's holding Robin up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you lose the ability to manipulate\Nthat vexing chain, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These penguins plan on freezing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll come in for\Nthe kill once we can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn it!\N--The beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, fall into a close formation\Nso we can share body heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is so wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working up a nasty sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! It's not like I want to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, do you feel nice and warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather fight than keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with him, Commander Stansen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is our flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first man to ever bring me\Nto my hands and knees, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You've still got some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're also the first\Nto have truly made me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Level Up: 5,500 Degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot Omelet Shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Accino...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan still hasn't given the sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which means we're stuck\Nreclaiming the flag ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does! We've gotta beat Luffy to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for our strategy meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't worried any!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, we've gotta get our flag back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're going to reclaim our--\Nthe Phoenix Pirates'--pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Uh-huh!\N--Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, it's horrible! Our ship pulled\Naway from the shore all on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave the ship to us!\NCaptain, you go with Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Stansen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one slippery brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're done for, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Hot-Hot Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's my move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your shots are moving\Nat the same speed as earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupid! Hurry and run for it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That startled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about your bounty anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to melt you into nothing but steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't 300-million-Berry\Nsteam sound luxurious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a sauna, Naked Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evaporate off the face of the planet, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, my darling\Ndaughter and sons were...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The temperature keeps climbing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is his Hot-Hot Fruit to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be more to it than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sanji, Franky's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about him!\NI'm sure he has plans of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the Savage Penguins' doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! They trashed our raiding dory,\Nso we can't go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they retaliating for how\Nwe took out their friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how messed up are these penguins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain and Jiro will\Ndefinitely get our Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to face them if they came back
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there wasn't a ship\Non which to hoist the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Stansen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Big Sister Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here with me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise that you won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, Lil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin-chan!\N--Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you do as I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that kid controlling the plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll give her a good spanking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are strictly prohibited from\Nraising your hand against a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a broad definition of the term...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unhand Robin-chan, you stinking flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you--! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your friends all that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I want to get our flag back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Crew's flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa enjoys collecting a bunch of Jolly Rogers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't care about those scraps of cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, they may be nothing\Nmore than scraps of cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to us pirates, our flag is\Nmore important than life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something we can't lose, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really all that important...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Papa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Save--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only saying this for your own good!\NYou'll get indigestion if you eat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lil!\N--Special Attack! Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister Robin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything were to happen to you,\Nyour big sister and brothers would be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're their cute, precious little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your family dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we on top of a...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second... Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the New World?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After I get our Jolly Roger back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get there. Your destination\Nwas set in stone a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided that's where I'm headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely going there after I kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let go, even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our pride as pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly Hot Nose Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! I... I made sure to get it! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Nami-san! Now Luffy\Nwon't make fun of--whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What's with that flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we get to start over from scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Robin, Sanji-kun,\Nand the others make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope ours isn't amongst those...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.59,0:22:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Lovely Land...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now my prized collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, I will personally take you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot-Hot powers, to the max!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.11,0:22:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum Heat Level: 10,000 Degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still heat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are those two up to?!\NThe ice is melting right and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're going all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm starting to get\Nconcerned about our Log Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're unbelievable! I guess I'll go\Npick them up in my super ship right quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll Be Waiting in the New World!\NParting with the Courageous Pirates"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
